1972;;One Is a Lonely Number;;American;;Mel Stuart;;Trish Van Devere, Monte Markham, Janet Leigh;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/One_Is_a_Lonely_Number;;The story follows Aimee Brower (Van Devere), who wakes and finds her husband has left her. After learning everything about why he did it, she then proceeds to put her life back together.